extendedInfo.description: **All new update coming soon!! With windows 8 and other cool features!**If your computer is not working right who wants to pay an arm and a leg for IT help, and chances are you are not able to look up the solution to the problem on the internet from your computer.  Thanks to Computer Helper Free you now can fix or troubleshoot a wide variety of problems without spending a ton of money to pay someone to fix it!  One of the biggest features of this app is the ability to submit a problem you are having and get a free response about how to fix it! Computer helper Free really does help you fix your computer with step by step instructions on how to fix the problem.  Computer Helper Free covers all the common operating systems.  The best part is, there will be weekly updates continually adding more and more computer problems to the list to help you troubleshoot problems.This app helps you with a wide ranges of things from the common problem "My Computer is Slow" to the mouse not working.  Also included  you get helpful tips and tricks, how toâs, and basic computer information to make your computer work better and your life easier!There are also weekly updates which will add more and more computer help problems, how to's, and helpful tips to the app.This is a new app and is going to be continually changing to meet your wants or preferences so give feedback in the app!If you want even more computer help and troubleshooting solutions download the Pro version for only 99 cents.Please rate this if this app helped you! Thanks for taking the time at my app!
